        <mxCell id="U3xCyMBUVf51coK3sNU9-5" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=#fff2cc;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;gradientColor=#ffd966;" value="&lt;b&gt;country_details_raw.sql:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. Config: materialized = table&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. run a pre_hook &quot;copy_json&quot; -&amp;gt; copies into table from&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;ext_stage(s3-snowflake-integration)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. schema_name: raw (macro generate_schema_name)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;i&gt;After config:&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. using CTE named as &#39;country_details_raw&#39; read from table&amp;nbsp; and dbt automatically creates table and insert those records.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
